00e9mon predecessor, with eight wings at the sides of its body. This Pok\u00e9mon swam in the primordial sea by undulating these eight wings."}, {"version": "black", "text": "A Pok\u00e9mon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws."}, {"version": "black-2", "text": "A Pok\u00e9mon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws."}, {"version": "diamond", "text": "A Pok\u00e9mon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws."}, {"version": "emerald", "text": "It was resurrected from a fossil using the power of science. It swims by undulating the eight wings at its sides. They were feet that adapted to life in the sea."}, {"version": "firered", "text": "It is a kind of POK\u00e9MON progenitor. It uses its extending claws to catch prey hiding among rocks on the seafloor."}, {"version": "heartgold", "text": "An ancestral Pok\u00e9mon that lived in the ocean. Over time, its eight feet transformed into wings."}, {"version": "leafgreen", "text": "It is a kind of POK\u00e9MON progenitor. It uses its extending claws to catch prey hiding among rocks on the seafloor."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "Anorith was regenerated from a prehistoric fossil. This primitive Pok\u00e9mon once lived in warm seas. It grips its prey firmly between its two large claws."}, {"version": "pearl", "text": "A Pok\u00e9mon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws."}, {"version": "platinum", "text": "A Pok\u00e9mon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws."}, {"version": "ruby", "text": "ANORITH was regenerated from a prehistoric fossil. This primitive POK\u00e9MON once lived in warm seas. It grips its prey firmly between its two large claws."}, {"version": "sapphire", "text": "ANORITH is said to be a type of POK\u00e9MON predecessor, with eight wings at the sides of its body. This POK\u00e9MON swam in the primordial sea by undulating these eight wings."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "Anorith can swim swiftly by pulling its eight wings through the water like oars on a boat. This Pok\u00e9mon is an ancestor of modern bug Pok\u00e9mon."}, {"version": "soulsilver", "text": "An ancestral Pok\u00e9mon that lived in the ocean. Over time, its eight feet transformed into wings."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "This Pok\u00e9mon was restored from a fossil. Anorith lived in the ocean about 100,000,000 years ago, hunting with its pair of claws."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "This is one kind of primeval bug Pok\u00e9mon. With eight wings, it could apparently swim a lot faster than you\u2019d expect."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "When restored Anorith are released into the ocean, they don\u2019t thrive, because the water composition has changed since their era."}, {"version": "white", "text": "A Pok\u00e9mon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "A Pok\u00e9mon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws."}, {"version": "x", "text": "It is a kind of Pok\u00e9mon progenitor. It uses its extending claws to catch prey hiding among rocks on the seafloor."}, {"version": "y", "text": "A Pok\u00e9mon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "diamond", "emerald", "firered", "heartgold", "leafgreen", "omega-ruby", "pearl", "platinum", "ruby", "sapphire", "shield", "soulsilver", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "brilliant-diamond-shining-pearl", "colosseum", "diamond-pearl", "emerald", "firered-leafgreen", "heartgold-soulsilver", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "platinum", "ruby-sapphire", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon"